OL,3,CMP and former deputy party chairman
OL,4,CLee Anderson has Tory whip suspended
OL,6,FThe former deputy party chairman lost
OL,7,Fthe Tory whip after refusing to
OL,8,Fapologise for the remarks and has said
OL,9,Fhe accepts he left the prime minister
OL,10,Fwith "no option" but to take action.
OL,12,FBut Mr Sunak is being pressed by Mr
OL,13,FKhan to stop what he described as
OL,14,F"moral rot" in the Conservative Party
OL,15,Fafter the comments prompted an outcry.
