OL,6,FThe Labour mayor said: "Although the
OL,7,Fwhip has been belatedly withdrawn from
OL,8,FLee Anderson, the silence from Rishi
OL,9,FSunak and the Cabinet and tacit
OL,10,Fendorsement of these vile remarks via
OL,11,FConservative briefings can't help but
OL,12,Flead to the conclusion that Muslims
OL,13,Fare fair game as far as the
OL,14,FConservative Party is concerned."
