OL,3,CMP and former deputy party chairman
OL,4,CLee Anderson has Tory whip suspended
OL,6,FIn an appearance on GB News on Friday,
OL,7,FMr Anderson had said: "I don't
OL,8,Factually believe that the Islamists
OL,9,Fhave got control of our country, but
OL,10,Fwhat I do believe is they've got
OL,11,Fcontrol of Khan and they've got
OL,12,Fcontrol of London... He's actually
OL,13,Fgiven our capital city away to his
OL,14,Fmates."
OL,16,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer
OL,17,Fwelcomed the action against Mr
OL,18,FAnderson but added that the prime
OL,19,Fminister's "weakness means Tory MPs
OL,20,Fcan act with impunity".
