OL,3,CMP and former deputy party chairman
OL,4,CLee Anderson has Tory whip suspended
OL,6,F"It's right that Lee Anderson has lost
OL,7,Fthe whip after his appalling racist
OL,8,Fand Islamophobic outburst against
OL,9,FSadiq Khan," Sir Keir wrote on X,
OL,10,Fformerly Twitter.
OL,12,F"But what does it say about the Prime
OL,13,FMinister's judgement that he made Lee
OL,14,FAnderson deputy chairman of his party?"
OL,16,F"Whether it is Liz Truss staying
OL,17,Fsilent on Tommy Robinson or Suella
OL,18,FBraverman's extreme rhetoric, Rishi
OL,19,FSunak's weakness means Tory MPs can
OL,20,Fact with impunity.
