OL,3,CMP and former deputy party chairman
OL,4,CLee Anderson has Tory whip suspended
OL,6,F"This isn't just embarrassing for the
OL,7,FConservative Party, it emboldens the
OL,8,Fworst forces in our politics. Rishi
OL,9,FSunak needs to get a grip and take on
OL,10,Fthe extremists in his party.
OL,12,F"The Tories may be getting more and
OL,13,Fmore desperate as the election
OL,14,Fapproaches, but Rishi Sunak has a
OL,15,Fresponsibility to stop this slide into
OL,16,Fever more toxic rhetoric."
