OL,3,CMP and former deputy party chairman
OL,4,CLee Anderson has Tory whip suspended
OL,6,FLabour Party chairwoman Anneliese
OL,7,FDodds described Mr Anderson's comments
OL,8,Fas "unambiguously Islamophobic,
OL,9,Fdivisive and damaging" and added it is
OL,10,F"right that he has had the whip
OL,11,Fremoved".
OL,13,FCabinet minister Grant Shapps earlier
OL,14,Fdistanced himself from the remarks but
OL,15,Fstopped short of condemning his fellow
OL,16,FMP, arguing that people should be
OL,17,Fallowed to "speak their mind".
